<i>noun</i>: 엄정 [엄정], 엄격성 [엄껵썽], 엄격 [엄껵] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>엄정 [엄정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictness; rigidness</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 바름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being strict and right.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fairness; impartiality</dd><br>
<dd>날카롭고 공정함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being sharp and fair.</dd><br>
<dt>엄격성 [엄껵썽]</dt><br>
<dd>rigidness; sternness; austerity</dd><br>
<dd>매우 엄하고 철저한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being very strict and thorough.</dd><br>
<dt>엄격 [엄껵]</dt><br>
<dd>rigidness; sternness; austerity</dd><br>
<dd>말, 태도, 규칙 등이 매우 엄하고 철저함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very strict and thorough in words, attitude, rules, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>